（EUV）。不过在 2021 年，荷兰还是向中国出口了价值 20 亿欧元的其他光刻机。 \t2022 年 10 月 7 日，拜登政府再度出台了一系列对华半导体产业的限制措施。美国彭博社曾援引消息人士的话称，美国官员一直在游说荷兰当局在禁止向中国出售最先进的极紫外线光刻机（EUV）基础上，进一步将禁售范围扩大到上一代技术深紫外线光刻机（DUV）的出口。 \t 对于此类游说，荷兰阿斯麦（ASML）去年 7 月在披露财报时 \t 荷兰政府对于美方施压也多次表示不满，强调荷兰将捍卫本国利益，不会照搬美国政策。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579210845"}}, "attached_info": "ClQItvCjlo2y5tUtEAMaCDkwOTk1MTAwIOiqmJ4GMAA4E0Akcgk1NzkyMTA4NDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1674292056.1539285", "card_id": "Q_576512378", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 189}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么容易宽恕、原谅别人的人更容易感到幸福？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c57e980fff6d02031b94489065b63013_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576512378"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItvCjlo2y5tUtEAMaCDkwMzk1MzkzINCAz50GMAQ46wFAJXIJNTc2NTEyMzc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1674292056.15441", "card_id": "Q_579676722", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "漫画家应不应该原封不动地按编辑提的意见去改作品？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "起因是集英社玛格丽特杂志的一位编辑说自己如果看到漫画家只照着自己的意见去改的话会感到很失望。 此话题引出了很多漫画大佬聊自己的经历。 ​​​"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2af10503dea136ce34905199b07e67c3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579